question_text: There are many ways to govern a country. Would you disapprove or approve of the following alternatives? Elections and Parliament are abolished so that the president can decide everything.
response_categories: 1 Strongly Disapprove / 2 Disapprove / 3 Neither Approve Nor Disapprove / 4 Approve / 5 Strongly Approve

question_text: Which of these three statements is closest to your own opinion?
response_categories: 1 Democracy is preferable to any other kind of government / 2 For someone like me, it does not matter what kind of government we have. / 3 Under some circumstances, an authoritarian government can be preferable to a democratic one
